Noel Johnson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Noel_Johnson 0 Noel Frank Johnson (28 December 1916 – 1 October 1999) was an English actor. He was the radio voice of Dick Barton special agent on BBC radio and Dan Dare on Radio Luxembourg. Noel_Frank_Johnson ( 28_December_1916 – 1_October_1999 ) was an_English_actor .
